FollowPermission - Class in com.example.feelslikemonday.model
This is a model class that contains a username of a candidate user and all of the usernames of users that have permission to follow this candidate user It has a followerUsername attribute which is the username of a candidate user It has a followeeUsernames attribute which is a list of usernames of users that have permission to follow the user with the username followerUsername

FollowRequest - Class in com.example.feelslikemonday.model
This class acts as a "table" to retrieve requests that have been sent to the user Follow requests keep track of the person requesting to follow another user and for the person receiving the request Sending requests can be reached from the main activity using the navigation drawer by clicking send requests Viewing and managing requests can be reached from the main activity using the navigation drawer by clicking Follower requests
